[vim setting] 

	git config --global user.name "sj_toy_proj"
	git config --global user.email again4you@gmail.com

	git config --global color.ui "auto"
	git config --global core.editor "vim"

	git config --global --list



[how to clone the git repogitory]

	git remote add origin git@github.com:again4you/sj_toy_proj.git
	git push origin master

	git clone git@github.com:again4you/sj_toy_proj



[Problems & Solutions]

again4you@againserver:~$ ssh -T git@github.com
Agent admitted failure to sign using the key.
Permission denied (publickey).

again4you@againserver:~$ ssh-add ~/.ssh/id_rsa
Identity added: /home/again4you/.ssh/id_rsa (/home/again4you/.ssh/id_rsa)
again4you@againserver:~$ ssh -T git@github.com
Hi again4you! You've successfully authenticated, but GitHub does not provide shell access.



